{"tid":2384452,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救！）個external hard drive用用下用唔到！","createTime":"2021-01-28T14:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T14:41:59.000Z","uid":71001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75681704b34fa0e62e9924cef5c642403c85d84b","tid":2384452,"uid":71001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCkJ3Ft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCkJ3Ft.jpg&h=1c036c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琴日我想用Toshiba個hard drive backup notebook 啲資料<br />\n<br />\n其實之前用過幾次都冇咩問題 今日用左半日都ok<br />\n之後係個hard drive㩒d片出黎 睇左啲片幾次之後都無咩問題嘅<br />\n但再㩒啲片就話我error 之後㩒其他文件都error<br />\n然後㩒安全退出就話我仲話我有文件開緊 唔俾我退出<br />\n咁我就直接unplug個hard drive (但我幾肯定我unplug前我close哂所有file)<br />\n<br />\n之後就大鑊啦 我想connect返個hard drive就唔得<br />\n一connect個hard drive係著燈既 電腦都話已連接<br />\n但主機就show唔到個hard drive 出黎<br />\n隔一陣部電腦就自動幫我disconnect埋個hard drive<br />\n然後話無法辨識裝置 驅動程式錯誤咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道點解會咁 點樣先開得返 我有好多document係入面架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0aaMEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0aaMEV.png&h=702d6630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/buB9hMK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbuB9hMK.png&h=f42e1a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEKSfyO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEKSfyO.png&h=e1135b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWPSfy7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWPSfy7.png&h=850d40f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fce59bfbc841b6b88b9da617538606892220bda","tid":2384452,"uid":173121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:38:39.000Z","msg":"試吓轉一個USB位插，<br />\n如果都係唔得即係舊嘢壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3d4cd35d11c970a428d6bb02cb7c4fdac100aa","tid":2384452,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"隻嘢已經error 你仲無視警告夾硬unplug<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2088f3b78b96d69eb2484cdc30b64db8fddbcb7c","tid":2384452,"uid":173121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fce59bfbc841b6b88b9da617538606892220bda","tid":2384452,"uid":173121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:38:39.000Z","msg":"試吓轉一個USB位插，<br />\n如果都係唔得即係舊嘢壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"或者你咪試吓插落第二部電腦度睇吓得唔得"},{"pid":"58a3e16b0e2a70fcdeee994602867ab6886cc7be","tid":2384452,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"試下拆咗入面隻hdd出嚟再用第二台機睇下read唔read到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}